{"tid":729491,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"壹週刊 被譏皮膚白像AV！STU48 森香穗直播哭訴經紀人性騷擾","createTime":"2018-07-04T15:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T03:55:48.000Z","uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0201ef1637c3c20a6aa05a1dd52efc0a4e2025","tid":729491,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"日本國民女團「AKB48」的姊妹團「STU48」，以兵庫及德島等瀨戶內地區為基地，透過船上劇場做為表演舞台，昨公布郵輪名稱為「STU48號」，但郵輪準備啟航之時，卻傳出21歲成員森香穗在直播中哭訴，遭劇場管理人言語性騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAzxshK.img?h=400&amp;w=600&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=326&amp;y=61\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAzxshK.img%3Fh%3D400%26w%3D600%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D326%26y%3D61&h=66145045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n森香穗前晚在官方直播平台「SHOWROOM」透露，劇場管理人山本學曾對她說：「STU48是樸素的團體，其他成員的皮膚偏黑很健康，但妳的膚色太白，看起來太豔麗，好像AV女優。」讓她心理受創，直播時邊說邊落淚，她難過表示：「我天生皮膚白，很難曬黑，而卡雲尼的空缺，或由史杜安尼或進攻中場迪阿拉辛達頂上。該怎麼辦，我也不知道。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAzzlS1.img?h=400&amp;w=500&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAzzlS1.img%3Fh%3D400%26w%3D500%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df&h=2110af6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友為她抱不平，痛斥山本學不該言語騷擾，還要求他直接離職。山本學之後在官網發文道歉，表示面談時說的話被誤解而導致誤會，自己並沒有那個意思，也對森香穗及粉絲感到抱歉，日後會深刻反省。"},{"pid":"874a3d23f7d6244a2bac8036e954d4719f5181aa","tid":729491,"uid":9681,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:07:32.000Z","msg":"啲圖做乜鳩"},{"pid":"18804daf31dac74a28b7eb45ec6722939d0cdedb","tid":729491,"uid":14208,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"若有若無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566e0768dea3353ff9fd89f04372f32be49217ea","tid":729491,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"負皮不解釋"},{"pid":"15501eaa1729cd436b6636ea5b374f532e0ff23f","tid":729491,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"無咗卡雲尼<br />\n烏龜等收皮"},{"pid":"8992ae7d696e715b33a34596ddf536845f97f8fa","tid":729491,"uid":74958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"點解無朱千雪？"},{"pid":"6961b7a7714778bfbbfdfe28b39edfd112e10e24","tid":729491,"uid":34495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3b97771df2f36abb6cf54de108ed0a8e707bd1","tid":729491,"uid":30145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:37:11.000Z","msg":"之前都剩係加段字 而家所有圖都轉埋 無人理原本單新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2232665bf996f8fbecac78ca4037e46a20829134","tid":729491,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"google一下樓主唔po圖係正確嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae66d29527511f190be952fad458eccf1ce81d7","tid":729491,"uid":106204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"我天生皮膚白，很難曬黑，而卡雲尼的空缺，或由史杜安尼或進攻中場迪阿拉辛達頂上。該怎麼辦，我也不知道。"},{"pid":"492701490dc5fdf9faa71ebf3ad4000e785f50ec","tid":729491,"uid":153497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而卡雲尼的空缺，或由史杜安尼或進攻中場迪阿拉辛達頂上。</span></span>"},{"pid":"ff4843cc1aac3be0ffbc42ecd042b3ba56224865","tid":729491,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":